I am glad there is a way to go past the TLC function, there are parts of my epic i could not do and quests i could not do.. and sometime's it gets so badly pathetic...<br>
For instance i was doing the cleric regent symbol quest, and muffed up so had to go back to the 2nd one... however the 2nd necklace is TLC and the 3rd necklace is not... so what? i am now permantly screwed or i get another cleric to do the quest for me - wich is against the whole point of the quest!!!<br>
<br>
It wasnt until i spent a few months bypassing TLC to do quests that i realise how much we lost haveing it implemented.<br>
